this, alledgedly, exploits the casimir effect to *create* a directional stream of particles thus producing thrust without using a stored propellant.<br>
<br>
current experiments produce rather less thrust than a gnat farting but as the old engineering saying goes &quot;If you can do it once, you can do it better&quot;  <br>
